title: Awesome Value! GREAT Location! Junior One Bedroom!
posting_body: ['1190 Mission Street at Trinity Place is a luxurious, modern building right in the center of SOMA.', 'Our well-designed apartment homes come equipped with full-size kitchens, including a dishwasher and garbage disposal.', 'The modern white cabinets on white walls and black granite countertops give our homes a trendy and sleek atmosphere.', 'The walnut laminate floors add warmth and texture.', 'The spacious floor plan in the junior one-bedroom apartment homes offers privacy with either a city or lush courtyard view.', 'You cannot go wrong in any home!', 'Our community has a large gym as well as a secluded outdoor plaza where you can picnic in the San Francisco sun.', 'We offer 24-hour front desk attendants as well as on-site maintenance for daily work orders and emergencies.', 'You will feel confident that you are in a home that provides all your needs.', 'In-person and virtual tours are available!', '3D Tour Link: <URL>', 'Features:', '-Whole Foods in our Community!!', '-Amazon Locker Package Room', '- Muni and BART stations on the same block', "-Walk Score of 95, Biker's Score of 97, Transit Score of 100", '-Walk-in closets', '-Granite countertops', '-Spectacular city views', '-Direct access from the building into the secluded Piazza courtyard', '-24-hour front desk associates', '-State-of-the-Art Fitness center', '-Laundry on every floor', '-Parking spaces available for rent in an enclosed garage', '-Direct access from the building into the garage', '-Pets allowed subject to company guidelines', '-No smoking', '-Pictures/Virtual tour of similar apartment shown', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers', 'do NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
